  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Uphold sexual minority rights in the great lakes</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">In the backdrop of tough anti gay laws regionally,and a discriminatory media stance,the project aims to shed light and demystify myths, hate speech and stereotypes targeting the LGBTI community in Rwanda and the great lakes region through advocacy, human rights education, legal aid and provision of psychosocial support with the intent to curb violation of basic human rights of this community and need for provision of equal opportunities and protection of rights like any other law abiding citizen</narrative>
  </description>
